org.jmol.g3d

Class Graphics3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmol.util.GData
      • org.jmol.g3d.Graphics3D

  • public final class Graphics3D
extends GData
    Provides high-level graphics primitives for 3D visualization for the software renderers. These methods should not have to be used with WebGL or OpenGL or other hardware accelerators. This module is linked to via reflection from org.jmol.viewer.Viewer Bob Hanson 9/2/2012

    A pure software implementation of a 3D graphics engine. No hardware required. Depending upon what you are rendering ... some people say it is pretty fast.
